description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a highly motivated individual with excellent communication skills to join the Oncology Booking Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be working within a team to support the smooth running of outpatient booking for patients at The Mid Yorkshire Hospitals NHS Trust. This will involve close liaison with a wide range of internal and external staff, particularly direct telephone conversations with patients on a daily basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will ensure that patients are treated in the appropriate settings and that outpatient clinics are utilised to capacity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder should be able to work independently, as well as working with the team to ensure patients are booked appropriately and timely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information or an informal visit, please contact Rebecca Cook: rebecca.cook10@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
